'''Terson Comfort Carriers''' was an [[Air taxi/Legends|air taxi]] company on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] around the time of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. It was established by [[Hasville Terson|Hasville]] and his wife, [[Adray Terson]].

